      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine condition. This example features the iconic S54 3.2L naturally aspirated straight-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and high-pressure Double VANOS. Power is managed by a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec variable M differential lock. The chassis is structurally sound with no subframe fatigue, featuring a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension for peerless turn-in response. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the aesthetic matches the mechanical excellence, retaining all original VIN tags and factory forged Style 67 wheels. A definitive driver\u2019s car for the discerning purist.",
