      "description": "Offering a collector-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in impeccable condition. This specimen is powered by the high-revving S54B32 inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure double-VANOS system that has been fully overhauled for optimal phase timing. Power is delivered via a Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission to a variable M-differential lock. The chassis integrity is absolute, featuring a proactive subframe reinforcement and a refreshed suspension with Bilstein B16 dampers and polyurethane bushings for razor-sharp turn-in. The exterior retains its factory luster with zero oxidation, while the cabin remains a time capsule. Mechanically flawless with perfect compression numbers and a documented service history, this is the definitive driver's machine for the serious enthusiast.",
